  18 Jan 2005; Simone Gotti <motaboy@gentoo.org>
  kdepim-kioslaves-3.4.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Remove sasl USE flag and make it a fixed dep. Fixes bug #78290.

  18 Jan 2005; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org>
  kdepim-kioslaves-3.4.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Added optional dep on cyrus-sasl. sasl is needed to build the sieve ioslave,
  and to enable authentication support in the imap4 ioslave.

*kdepim-kioslaves-3.4.0_beta1 (15 Jan 2005)

  15 Jan 2005; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +kdepim-kioslaves-3.4.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Adding the split ebuilds to portage. For KDE 3.4, we've created separate
  ebuilds for all the KDE apps.

